{"title":"Neumonía por Pneumocystis jiroveci (PCP)-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Neumología/Neumonía por Pneumocystis jiroveci (PCP)-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Neumonía por Pneumocystis jiroveci\\N(PCP)","guid":"BFjsBS0QRGZQelOGC2ZRrA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Perlas","guid":"KkRXLGAJBI1CPZ1bE04HTg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"¿Cuál es el principal factor de riesgo para desarrollar PCP?","guid":"DAod21pHfyYvsHpNCOSP3A","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Inmunosupresión, principalmente por VIH con recuento de CD4 < 200 céls/µL. (1)","guid":"JxVirgyQQFZkhkiScVGOBg","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"¿Cuál es la triada clásica de PCP?","guid":"bVh4GTS1lfsXdvpVDcXC0A","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Disnea, fiebre e infiltrados pulmonares difusos. (2)","guid":"MmIFGztnRJk5Ux8zYTDCLw","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"¿Cuál es el tratamiento de primera línea para PCP?","guid":"OUXv2l6f0yQoOiUlY4pHBw","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"Trimetoprim-sulfametoxazol (TMP-SMX) por vía oral o intravenosa. (3)","guid":"KGiS_Ez7ph1dwdOMNytDLA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"Definición","guid":"fOjNogyR7k87ozQBGaDeAA","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"Infección oportunista causada por el hongo Pneumocystis jiroveci (previamente conocido como Pneumocystis\\Ncarinii), que afecta a pacientes inmunocomprometidos, principalmente a aquellos con VIH/SIDA. (1)","guid":"PqjXsWp3woB22E5VO5GlUw","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"E-0FVX53d5B5YnbxTxsTmg","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"P. jiroveci: hongo atípico, coloniza alvéolos pulmonares, causa respuesta inflamatoria. (4)","guid":"BfOiczPaFmQB6Os9Q4b__w","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"Inmunosupresión → proliferación descontrolada de P. jiroveci. (4)","guid":"cP3SNHxViTRDHYMfbSuasA","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"P. jiroveci se adhiere a neumocitos tipo I mediante glicoproteínas de superficie. (23)","guid":"bGjCgC0fvs91XxX1L-Rqrw","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"10","text":"Neumocitos tipo I dañados → ↓ producción de surfactante. (23)","guid":"OLj2O0LeM98laFTjDiNOiA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"Neumocitos tipo II: hiperplasia compensatoria, producen membrana hialina. (23)","guid":"OTM7cwudWM8X1oo2TzZ7CA","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"10","text":"Membrana hialina + ↓ surfactante → colapso alveolar, ↓ compliance pulmonar. (23)","guid":"HhUbxkzcWhY3Y3T1MgIhHA","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"10","text":"Infiltración de células inflamatorias (macrófagos, neutrófilos, linfocitos CD4+) → daño alveolar difuso. (24)","guid":"S1PRpjDF6-YBHTS2Iq2Saw","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"10","text":"Daño alveolar difuso → ↑ permeabilidad alvéolo-capilar, edema intersticial y alveolar. (24)","guid":"BnPAZh9moaESCrg2DGdi2Q","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"10","text":"Edema y colapso alveolar → ↓ intercambio gaseoso, hipoxemia, ↑ gradiente alvéolo-arterial de O2. (24)","guid":"U0C4BRPzo3NP7mLYRD6KOQ","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"10","text":"Hipoxemia → vasoconstricción pulmonar hipóxica, hipertensión pulmonar, cor pulmonale. (25)","guid":"EEkspxML5fcxaiTpfLHvJw","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"10","text":"Resolución: regeneración de neumocitos tipo I y II, clearance de P. jiroveci por macrófagos alveolares. (26)","guid":"QCukxibJOt4sllnWeOSbAQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"10","text":"Complicaciones: fibrosis pulmonar por activación de fibroblastos y depósito de colágeno. (27)","guid":"aaduvVH-rroHB-mJItqqMQ","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"10","text":"Referencias","guid":"V1nAxFWt1H8eSWzrb10lyw","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"4. Clin Microbiol Rev.\\N2011;24(4):633-654.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"23. Semin Respir Crit Care\\NMed. 2012;33(5):543-554.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"24. Clin Chest Med.\\N2017;38(4):693-702.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"23","text":"25. Curr Opin Pulm Med.\\N2013;19(3):252-258.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"23","text":"26. Front Immunol.\\N2019;10:2213.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"23","text":"27. Semin Respir Crit Care\\NMed. 2012;33(5):543-554.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"0","text":"Beneficio fisiopatológico del uso\\Nde corticoides en PCP","guid":"JODzbTKB9VsiOyyxOcYg2Q","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"Corticoides → ↓ respuesta inflamatoria exagerada en PCP. (28)","guid":"bRMM5jRf0iUTHE8beF2-1g","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"Mecanismos\\Nde acción:","guid":"SyKEEWiTe8n526VomP8OnA","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"↓ producción de citoquinas proinflamatorias (IL-1, IL-6, TNF-α) por macrófagos alveolares. (29)","guid":"RIftmF2IJNJhRHhPc458yg","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"↓ quimiotaxis y activación de neutrófilos y linfocitos CD4+. (29)","guid":"GgUfw0XcVRgOT9nTf_a04g","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"↓ permeabilidad alvéolo-capilar y edema pulmonar. (30)","guid":"WCd2TWAf1lhAItAWGUMQpA","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"32","text":"↓ formación de membrana hialina y fibrosis pulmonar. (31)","guid":"C6wExGD9McUolcW-Iv8dTg","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"30","text":"Efectos clínicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"↓ hipoxemia y ↓ gradiente alvéolo-arterial de O2. (32)","guid":"bu08yFlgTaA6DMNpOeFT9w","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"↓ necesidad de ventilación mecánica. (32)","guid":"b-Eyg2EeI7tU5V1JHYKZUA","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"↓ mortalidad (RR 0.54, IC 95% 0.38-0.79). (33)","guid":"FOUtbAAk_YQJDbzlAfg6Ug","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"30","text":"Indicaciones:","guid":"Rn-hXYKyz9Qp7NGN6wBZ9g","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"PCP moderada a severa (PaO2 < 70 mmHg o gradiente\\Nalvéolo-arterial de O2 > 35 mmHg). (34)","guid":"NITPqRwqDAF6VfkoeQy9QQ","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Iniciar dentro de las primeras 72 horas del diagnóstico. (34)","guid":"ebIw01uacXdsmzoLE7dQlg","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"30","text":"Esquema:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"Prednisona 40 mg c/12h VO por 5 días, luego 40 mg/día por 5 días,\\Nluego 20 mg/día hasta completar 21 días. (34)","guid":"IXbGj3rrE94TrgV4eZ483A","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"Metilprednisolona 75% de la dosis de prednisona si uso IV. (34)","guid":"WwrqNlPQ1Y4S4U2AZrbu-w","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"30","text":"Precauciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"Monitorizar glicemia y presión arterial.","guid":"NM4HUzt3Ez4JtgxJI7tEGw","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"Considerar profilaxis para infecciones oportunistas\\N(candidiasis, reactivación de CMV).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"30","text":"Referencias","guid":"FNdg3kPCz7JdnJgSBLiTYQ","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"28. Chest. 1990;\\N98(6):1268-1270.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"29. Am J Respir Cell Mol Biol.\\N1994;10(4):430-436.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"30. J Immunol. 2000;\\N164(4):2131-2141.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"50","text":"31. Semin Respir Crit Care\\NMed. 2012;33(5):543-554.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"50","text":"32. N Engl J Med. 1990;\\N323(21):1451-1457.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"50","text":"33. Cochrane Database Syst\\NRev. 2006;(3):CD006150.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"50","text":"34. Clin Infect Dis. 2009;\\N48(Suppl 1):S1-S35.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"eohgaw1Nj5gnkxJXZ-DYhQ","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"En Chile, la incidencia de PCP en pacientes con VIH es de aproximadamente 10-15 casos por 100. 000 habitantes por año. (5)","guid":"XZwHiR7ec79yESU5e7EjUA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"La mortalidad por PCP en pacientes con VIH varía entre 10-30%, dependiendo de la gravedad y el acceso a tratamiento. (6)","guid":"a7rN1il0mi4ts0RsNw6ffA","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo","guid":"QgMllD8KDKx1pptVamu4kA","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"VIH/SIDA con recuento de CD4 < 200 céls/µL (RR: 5-10). (1)","guid":"MghCBknRIOEo1emrcLEZtw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Otras causas de inmunosupresión: neoplasias hematológicas, trasplante de órganos, uso de corticosteroides o inmunosupresores. (7)","guid":"WjqGFS7QeSJZvDHnYK5Gew","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"0","text":"Clínica","guid":"NEjjYR-uOAAsQr8LK1KUMQ","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Inicio insidioso con disnea progresiva, fiebre y tos seca. (2)","guid":"Oy4ORFjiSTRcS12OTy5ZUQ","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"Auscultación pulmonar: crepitantes finos difusos (Signo de Gellman). (2)","guid":"GANlBjBFzfMVkKl5EovFcg","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"Hipoxemia y alcalosis respiratoria en gases arteriales. (2)","guid":"PZNdjD0ju9B6bJ33f5aDIA","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"Factores de mal pronóstico: PaO2 < 60 mmHg, LDH > 500 U/L, albúmina < 3 g/dL. (8)","guid":"fC3IfHATOUxqAjuwCDN7RQ","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"64","text":"Complicaciones: insuficiencia respiratoria, neumotórax, neumomediastino. (9)","guid":"Q3uoLguZN2xNfx3pdYPqNA","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"64","text":"Disociación clínico-radiológica: disnea desproporcionada en relación a los hallazgos en la radiografía de tórax. (18)","guid":"VWpYTXZVB5RmNQPsCbM7rg","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"64","text":"Manifestaciones crónicas: fibrosis pulmonar, enfermedad pulmonar difusa (EPD), insuficiencia respiratoria crónica. (19)","guid":"FgM_lRJ3wvc1Bc_gaCz57A","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"0","text":"Estudio","guid":"Uim6VwF1Ql5JcaewETV9BQ","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Radiografía de tórax: infiltrados intersticiales difusos bilaterales, patrón en \"vidrio esmerilado\". (10)","guid":"Tjcaw2vG6h1tFalUIXfSyA","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"TC de tórax: opacidades en vidrio esmerilado, quistes o neumatoceles, engrosamiento septal interlobulillar. (10)","guid":"f7qNkD0EDCxltl0BEAO6Nw","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"Lavado broncoalveolar: tinción con metenamina de plata o inmunofluorescencia para P. jiroveci. (11)","guid":"UA_yIxcggeoMtalfEDuW6Q","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"B-D-glucano sérico elevado (sensibilidad 92%, especificidad 86%). (12)","guid":"Pem8yDlMAzUJIDHqJ5Erhg","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"72","text":"Laboratorio: elevación de LDH (> 500 U/L), hipoxemia (PaO2 < 60 mmHg), alcalosis respiratoria. (20)","guid":"C0qx7xAoG3NKa9W3aOa5eQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"R3L1mDYUVFRgOH_JQSUmaw","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"Clínico-radiológico en el contexto de inmunosupresión, confirmado por lavado broncoalveolar o biopsia transbronquial. (11)","guid":"ZfGVHxJLITVRz_yFQCwbNA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"Criterios diagnósticos: (14)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Clínica compatible.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"Infiltrados pulmonares típicos en radiografía o TC de tórax.","guid":"QRuaVyuMLmwg2mGvD1K1Gg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"Identificación de P. jiroveci en muestras respiratorias o tejido pulmonar.","guid":"F1MYig3wCwMwyofiFw2mGg","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"78","text":"Gold standard: visualización de quistes o trofozoítos de P. jiroveci en lavado broncoalveolar o biopsia. (11)","guid":"SvQXLxaA5OMnEWBSGwQJUg","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos\\Ndiferenciales","guid":"Ea7FzEzTudVU3HcCMyWMWw","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"Neumonía intersticial: (15)","guid":"R77Ns2iKfHosw8k4Ism36g","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"Neumonía viral (CMV, VRS)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"Neumonía por otros hongos\\N(Aspergillus, Cryptococcus)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"Toxoplasmosis pulmonar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"86","text":"Tuberculosis miliar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"86","text":"Sarcoidosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"86","text":"Neumonitis por fármacos","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación de\\Nseveridad: (21)","guid":"PFtSCT-lFrgJgKblcSlZXA","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"Leve: PaO2 > 70 mmHg, saturación de O2 > 94% con aire ambiental.","guid":"exwp9xM2sy4U5J14D_OK1Q","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"Moderada: PaO2 50-70 mmHg, saturación de O2 90-94% con aire ambiental.","guid":"VvmC4XKBNYoUrB43e9p2Tg","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"93","text":"Severa: PaO2 < 50 mmHg, saturación de O2 < 90% con aire ambiental, o necesidad de ventilación mecánica.","guid":"JQMq5jbnSug1oJcoV6odxQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"YjA0f3Fe8lQ-1eBOKaMqFw","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Objetivo: erradicar la infección y prevenir insuficiencia respiratoria.","guid":"J3NGqB8OYBdqyFCDOSIMdA","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"No farmacológico: oxigenoterapia para mantener SaO2 > 90%. (3)","guid":"a-IZ7D-kx4VsR5jQM6DnoA","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"Farmacológico: (3)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"Primera línea: TMP-SMX 15-20 mg/kg/día de TMP y\\N75-100 mg/kg/día de SMX, vía oral o IV, por 21 días.","guid":"WLB4wF_rRm9Vs-9lU8yitw","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"Efectos adversos: rash, fiebre, leucopenia, trombocitopenia, hepatitis.","guid":"cyH5nWqYjN1jwC2NSht8fg","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"Interacciones: warfarina, metotrexato, fenitoína.","guid":"XRnCZ3hsS8RF9fLNAhztTQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"Ajustar dosis en falla renal. Metabolismo hepático (CYP2C9).","guid":"L1OWrHuWifVZxwsTEYPLLA","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"Nombre comercial: Bactrimel. Precio: $2.000 por comprimido, $42.000 tratamiento completo.","guid":"bPV8SRic62E7JvVDFGjC8Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"100","text":"Segunda línea (intolerancia a TMP-SMX): Clindamicina 600 mg c/8h IV o 300-450 mg c/6-8h VO + Primaquina 30 mg/día VO, por 21 días.","guid":"KC9D_xkLYghWap-KZIqWCA","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"100","text":"Adyuvante en casos severos: Prednisona 40 mg c/12h VO por 5 días, luego disminuir gradualmente.","guid":"N6tLeCXvRcZNis9mI41lZQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"97","text":"Uso de corticoides: indicado en casos moderados a severos (PaO2 < 70 mmHg o gradiente alvéolo-arterial de O2 > 35 mmHg).\\NPrednisona 40 mg c/12h VO por 5 días, luego 40 mg/día por 5 días, luego 20 mg/día hasta completar 21 días. (22)","guid":"ZZQNSznSaDZXLk0FDcNRSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento y\\Npronóstico","guid":"deui6D0g_ONtaqIeUXMB7w","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"Radiografía de tórax y gases arteriales a las 48-72h para evaluar respuesta. (3)","guid":"Ut3KPi2Y7I9yTedTK45C_g","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"Consulta de seguimiento a las 2 semanas post-tratamiento. (3)","guid":"DYQy_kgB1rh_WuW2AKYsmw","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"109","text":"Mortalidad intrahospitalaria 10-30%. Factores de mal pronóstico: PaO2 < 60 mmHg, LDH > 500 U/L. (6)(8)","guid":"MppjlWMbE0NKwakaD7Ql_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"0","text":"Prevención","guid":"TdiYyn87tWlcTfeiWia-pg","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"Profilaxis primaria con TMP-SMX en pacientes con VIH y CD4 < 200 céls/µL. (16)","guid":"W4dfBxC3m-cR0RNKCtr1sw","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"Tratamiento antirretroviral y reconstitución inmune en pacientes con VIH. (16)","guid":"DE4l3GuYHl0cXsDfeUOiJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"0","text":"Tamizaje","guid":"atPTxnisuIJTamDLbwjdhQ","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"No recomendado de forma rutinaria. En pacientes con VIH, monitorizar recuento de CD4. (16)","guid":"BDUJvleFtiMNrGUWO-BVNw","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"0","text":"Aspectos\\Ngeriátricos","guid":"UDJupWEWxeIq6TK8Tadqjg","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"Mayor riesgo de efectos adversos a TMP-SMX. Considerar ajuste de dosis. (17)","guid":"fXT76Vs3NHxfbbqcYwkJNQ","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"Presentación atípica: menor fiebre, más compromiso del estado general. (17)","guid":"FQmcsjacB6FwzFqAZ-dm8A","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"118","text":"Mayor mortalidad (20-50%). Manejo precoz y agresivo. (17)","guid":"ZDT0MGMaQdMTdanvcbknLg","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"KxwYjBLQj6VyX1PJXbZ8IQ","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"1. Respir Med. 2010;\\N104(12):1767-1783.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"2. Semin Respir Crit Care Med.\\N2019;40(3):314-322.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"3. Cochrane Database Syst Rev.\\N2017;1(1):CD006150.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"122","text":"4. Clin Microbiol Rev.\\N2011;24(4):633-654.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"122","text":"5. Rev Chilena Infectol.\\N2015;32(2):199-205.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"122","text":"6. PLoS One. 2013;\\N8(10):e75574.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"122","text":"7. Transplant Proc. 2011;\\N43(6):2465-2469.","guid":"","c